    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been meticulously cared for by a single owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine, and the interior remains in pristine state, smelling like new with no signs of wear on the leather or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect; it has a full service history, and every component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model, offering a smooth, quiet, and reliable driving experience for the most discerning buyer.",
